            We have reserved a block of rooms at the Ortner Center located on the Union College Campus. 
            You may make reservations by calling 402-486-2545 and mentioning Needles-Origas Wedding. 
            For more information on rooms and pricing options, please visit the <a href="https://www.ucollege.edu/campus-services/ortner-center/guest-rooms">Ortner Center's website</a>.
